name: Cpanel entropysearch enum users
body:
### Cpanel entropysearch enum users.
These are my practice repositories containing many versions (on different languages) of popular CVEs/OSVDBs. It is both a project oriented to those who want to learn exploiting the hands-on way, and for those who want to suit a vulnerability with their specific-language knowledge.

```
$ git clone https://github.com/MauroEldritch/cpanel_entropysearch_enum_users
```
### About
Nothing special. If you feel like hiring a Security Eng, both locally or remotely, take a look at [my site](www.eldritch.com.ar).
